# C# & Unity Rules
- Fields: `[SerializeField] private _camelCase`; avoid public fields.
- Types/methods: `PascalCase`.
- Async: Unity `Awaitable` only; avoid `async Task`.
- Prefer Event Channels + Composition Root/Simple Injector for decoupling (no global service locator).
- Cache dependencies in `Awake`; no `GetComponent` in `Update`.
- Pool high-frequency objects with `UnityEngine.Pool.ObjectPool<T>`.
- Avoid UI string churn; use `StringBuilder` for frequent TMP updates.
- Tests: NUnit + AAA; logic in `Tests/EditMode`, scene/physics in `Tests/PlayMode`.
